    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-12-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-12-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="431"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d431">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1" type="from"
                            >Roosevelt</persName> to President <persName corresp="#p_II1" type="to"
                            >Inönü</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Cairo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-03">December 3,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear President <persName corresp="#p_II1"
                            >Inonu</persName>
                    </hi>, I am sending one of my own planes to meet you and your party in Adana,
                    together with my son-in-law, Major <persName corresp="#p_BJ3">John
                        Boettiger</persName>, who will hand this to you.</p>
                <p>The plane is in command of Major <persName corresp="#p_BOF1">Otis F.
                        Bryan</persName>.</p>
                <p>I hope you will have a smooth trip and I am looking forward with great pleasure
                    to seeing you on Saturday afternoon.</p>
                <p>Very sincerely yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">F[<hi rend="smallcaps">ranklin</hi>] D R[<hi
                                rend="smallcaps">oosevelt</hi>]</persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
